::Feline::

She walked around the lab, thinking.  She had Skulletron and 
Chordate.  Now she had HotRod.  She smiled.  She sent a message to 
the bridge, "If any other bots need repairs, sent them to the CR lab, 
I'll be waiting to help."  SHe knew the message would play on the 
bridge until it was recieved.  She sat on the stool and leaned back 
against the counter.  She was very pleased.  Her day was going very 
well.
